sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 用户
    participant Pricing as 定价页 (ModernPricing)
    participant Checkout as /api/creem/checkout
    participant Creem as Creem.io
    participant Webhook as /api/webhook/creem
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant TM as /astria/train-model
    participant Astria as Astria API
    participant TWH as /astria/train-webhook
    participant PWH as /astria/prompt-webhook

    %% ============================================
    %% Phase 1: 支付流程
    %% ============================================
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,DB: === Phase 1: 用户选择套餐并完成支付 ===
        User->>Pricing: 浏览三档套餐卡片
        User->>Pricing: 点击 Professional $49 按钮
        Pricing->>Checkout: POST {tier: 'professional'}
        Checkout->>Checkout: 校验登录状态
        Checkout->>Checkout: CREEM_PRODUCT_IDS['professional']<br/>→ 'prod_198ewWuQouDaQfEOT6kTvj'
        Checkout->>Creem: POST /v1/checkouts<br/>{product_id, request_id: userId}
        Creem-->>Checkout: {checkout_url}
        Checkout-->>Pricing: {url: 'https://creem.io/...'}
        Pricing->>Creem: 跳转至 Creem 支付页
        User->>Creem: 完成信用卡支付
        Creem->>Webhook: POST webhook (checkout.completed)<br/>{eventType, object: {request_id, order: {product: 'prod_198ewWuQ...'}}}
        Webhook->>Webhook: HMAC-SHA256 签名验证
        Webhook->>Webhook: PRODUCT_ID_TO_TIER['prod_198ewWuQ...']<br/>→ 'professional'
        Webhook->>DB: UPSERT credits<br/>SET credits=credits+1, tier='professional'
        Webhook->>DB: INSERT INTO orders<br/>(user_id, creem_product_id, tier, amount_cents)
        Webhook-->>Creem: 200 OK
    end

    %% ============================================
    %% Phase 2: 训练流程
    %% ============================================
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,Astria: === Phase 2: 用户上传图片并启动训练 ===
        User->>TM: 上传 4-10 张自拍照片
        User->>TM: 点击 "开始训练" 按钮
        TM->>TM: 并行上传图片至 Supabase Storage
        TM->>DB: SELECT tier FROM credits WHERE user_id=userId
        DB-->>TM: {tier: 'professional'}
        TM->>TM: getTrainingConfig('professional')<br/>→ branch='sd15'<br/>→ primaryPack='corporate-headshots'<br/>→ additionalPacks=['partners-headshots','natural-headshots']
        TM->>DB: INSERT INTO models<br/>(user_id, name, type, tier='professional')<br/>→ modelId=42
        TM->>Astria: POST /p/corporate-headshots/tunes<br/>{tune: {branch:'sd15', image_urls,<br/>callback: trainWebhookUrl}}
        Astria-->>TM: 201 Created {tune_id: 999}
        TM->>DB: INSERT INTO samples (modelId=42, uri) × N
        TM->>DB: UPDATE credits SET credits=credits-1
        TM-->>User: ✓ 训练已提交！预计 ~25 分钟
    end

    %% ============================================
    %% Phase 3: 训练完成回调
    %% ============================================
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Astria,TWH: === Phase 3: Astria 训练完成 → Webhook 回调 ===
        Note over Astria: ~25 分钟训练 + corporate prompts 生成
        Astria->>TWH: POST train-webhook<br/>{tune: {id: 999, name: 'man', ...}}
        TWH->>TWH: 校验 webhook_secret

        TWH->>DB: SELECT tier FROM models WHERE id=42
        DB-->>TWH: {tier: 'professional'}

        TWH->>DB: UPDATE models<br/>SET modelId='999', status='finished'

        Note over TWH: === 根据 tier 触发额外 Pack ===

        alt tier = 'starter'
            Note over TWH: 无额外 — 仅 corporate (已完成)

        else tier = 'professional'
            TWH->>Astria: 触发 partners-headshots Pack<br/>使用 tune_id=999
            Astria->>PWH: prompt callback: partners images
            PWH->>DB: INSERT images (partners-headshots)

            TWH->>Astria: 触发 natural-headshots Pack<br/>使用 tune_id=999
            Astria->>PWH: prompt callback: natural images
            PWH->>DB: INSERT images (natural-headshots)

        else tier = 'executive'
            TWH->>Astria: 触发 4 个额外 Pack prompts<br/>branch='flux', resolution=1024×1024
            loop partners, natural, speaker, realtor
                Astria->>PWH: prompt callback: images
                PWH->>DB: INSERT images
            end
        end

        TWH->>User: 发送邮件通知：训练完成！
    end

    %% ============================================
    %% Phase 4: 展示结果
    %% ============================================
    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over User,DB: === Phase 4: 用户查看生成的头像 ===
        User->>DB: 查看模型详情页
        DB-->>User: 展示所有生成的图片<br/>Professional 套餐 · 3 种风格 · ~100 张
        User->>User: 浏览、下载头像
    end
